<br>
The Miken Ultra Maxload and Balanced Load bats were voluntarily pulled from possible approval by Miken. The Miken Ultra II failed the old bpf standard as well as it failed the new bpf standard.<br>
<br>
Louisville Slugger simply did not offer either model of the Genesis SB103 &amp; SB34 for approval.<br>
<br>
The Easton Synergy did not pass the old bpf standard nor the new bpf standard.<br>
<br>
