To All Consumers affected by the NSA ban of the Easton SCX2 Synergy:<br>
<br>
The Easton SCX2 Synergy bat has been banned by the National Softball Association (NSA). It remains legal for play in the other three major softball associations (ASA, USSSA, ISA). <br>
